summary:
David Dobrik's most absurd adventures (the ones I remember, so feel free to add):
The bdsm sex party (the one where Jason took...
body:
David Dobrik’s most absurd adventures (the ones I remember, so feel free to add):

  • The bdsm sex party (the one where Jason took Molly and came back home at 7 A.M.)
  • When someone was using his name to send terrorist threats and the FBI went to his parents’ house
  • Flying to America alone when he was five (I felt like this had to be here lol)
  • Driving with an expired license, no insurance, no plate and not getting arrested
  • When a teenage girl on acids attacked him
  • His house being haunted and he and Natalie waking up with the same black marks behind their necks
  • The wizard doctor his mum made him go to
  • The one time a guy broke into his home, shat on his couch and stole Corinna’s merch
  • And obviously he married his best friend’s 75 yo mum to be his stepdad
